    "### A: Generate Dataset\n",
    "* $Class_0$: Uniformly distributed in the (union of) 3 squares: $[-1, 0]~x~[-1, 0] + [-1, 0]~x~[0, 1] + [0, 1]~x~[-1, 0]$\n",
    "* $Class_1$: Gaussian distributed centered at $(0.5, 0.5)$, with variance $(0.5, 0.5)$\n",
    "* Generate 150 points in $Class_0$ and 50 points in $Class_1$."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
